          14:  31
          15:  25
          16:  17
          17:  28

9. Class Distribution: (2 classes)
   1. 45.2 percent are democrat
   2. 54.8 percent are republican

Class predictiveness and predictability: Pr(C|A=V) and Pr(A=V|C)
